{"tid":2057193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"The Pulse 新疆再教育營專題於美國國際電影及電視節奪奬","createTime":"2020-06-09T08:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T14:28:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa32caad8382279be4ea3e4c854edc4cea084bba","tid":2057193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/102370382_3154270331282663_905336860527042091_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=ca45BwPZe2gAX_KDd7d&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=805421620d2dbd1ab33cafd87508b79c&amp;oe=5F03B507\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F102370382_3154270331282663_905336860527042091_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3Dca45BwPZe2gAX_KDd7d%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D805421620d2dbd1ab33cafd87508b79c%26oe%3D5F03B507&h=6185d17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRTHK's The Pulse<br />\n&middot; 3 hrs &middot; <br />\n <br />\n📢📢 The Pulse has won a Certificate for Creative Excellence in the US International Film &amp; Video Festival in Documentary: Public Affairs Programs for &ldquo;In the Prisons that Don&rsquo;t Exist&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\nThe documentary tells the stories of the Uyghurs and Kazakhs who were detained in the &ldquo;re-education camps&rdquo; in Xinjiang, China. The Chinese authorities argued, in the name of combating terrorism and religious separatism, those are &ldquo;vocational training camps&rdquo; instead. However, human rights advocates say this is part of a deliberate attempt to destroy the cultural identity of Uyghurs and other ethnic minorities.<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\nWatch the award-winning story here:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;In the Prisons that Don&rsquo;t Exist&rdquo;<br />\nPart 1: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2xIOQuE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xIOQuE&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=c3b5718d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2xIOQuE</a><br />\n<br />\nPart 2: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3517Q3n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3517Q3n&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=cd8dfba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3517Q3n</a><br />\n<br />\nPart 3: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3eOvuF8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3eOvuF8&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=50a11a42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3eOvuF8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your continuous support! &mdash; celebrating success."},{"pid":"69b864ca04229b9e21b0f34332f95d048178936a","tid":2057193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa26ee81d8bac02511464499ebc6d3e10c08783","tid":2057193,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3679954df3ba2fad2e652d8c92ecdaf5542b724b","tid":2057193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa26ee81d8bac02511464499ebc6d3e10c08783","tid":2057193,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src